## Key Interactions to Verify

- **Quick Pitch modal**: Click → opens → displays mission/metrics → "Want more detail?" button → smooth scroll to full site
- **Deep Dive CTA**: Click → scrolls directly to projects/blog sections without modal
- **Holographic card tilt**: Desktop hover → 3D perspective transform → smooth return on mouse leave
- **Device adaptation**: Resize browser desktop → mobile → WebGL gracefully degrades to CSS-only, no performance issues
- **WebGL context loss**: Background tab for 10min → return → context lost detected → fallback UI → context recovered → particles re-enable after cooldown
- **Blog MDX rendering**: New post with frontmatter → Zod validation → build succeeds → renders with syntax highlighting
- **Performance degradation**: Slow device → frame time >20ms for 3 frames → particles disable → frame time improves → 5s cooldown → particles re-enable
- **Keyboard navigation**: Tab through page → focus visible on all interactive elements → Enter activates buttons → Escape closes modal
- **Screen reader**: Navigate with NVDA/VoiceOver → ARIA labels announced → dynamic content changes announced

## Edge Cases

- **Invalid blog frontmatter**: Missing required fields (title, date, tags, excerpt) → build fails with clear Zod error message
- **Very long blog post**: 10,000 word article → page renders without timeout, scroll performance maintained, TOC navigation works
- **No WebGL support**: Old browser or disabled GPU → falls back to CSS-only holographic effects, site remains functional
- **Mobile landscape vs portrait**: Orientation change → layout adapts correctly, no horizontal scroll, touch targets remain accessible
- **Concurrent modals**: User triggers Quick Pitch while another overlay is open → modal stacking prevented, only one active at a time
- **Rapid window resize**: Quick resize desktop → mobile → desktop multiple times → device detection debounced, no layout thrash, no React state errors
- **Arc reactor mouse parallax**: Rapid mouse movements → parallax follows smoothly with 100ms delay, no jank, no memory leak
- **Blog post with no images**: Frontmatter complete, no images in post → renders cleanly, no broken image placeholders
- **Chromatic aberration trigger**: Page load → hero entrance → chromatic aberration fires → only fires once per session (not on every scroll)

## Critical Paths

1. **VC Journey (Primary)**:
   - Land on homepage → see "Quick Pitch" CTA → click → modal appears with mission/metrics → impressed → click "Want more detail?" → smooth scroll to full site → see projects/blog → understand technical depth → reach out via contact form

2. **Engineer Journey (Secondary)**:
   - Land on homepage → see "Deep Dive" CTA → click → scroll to full site → browse projects → click project card → navigate to /projects/[slug] → read technical details → click through to blog post → see architecture deep-dive → impressed by technical depth → reach out

3. **Mobile Experience (50% of users)**:
   - Visit on phone → clean CSS-only UI loads fast (<2s) → no WebGL (performance) → navigate blog → read posts smoothly → tap contact → form works on mobile → can reach out

4. **Accessibility Journey (WCAG 2.1 AA)**:
   - Navigate with keyboard only → tab through page → all interactive elements reachable → focus indicators visible → activate with Enter/Space → screen reader announces all content → `prefers-reduced-motion` disables animations → complete site accessible

5. **Performance Recovery**:
   - Desktop user on low-end device → WebGL renders → frame time degrades → particles auto-disable → performance improves → particles re-enable after 5s cooldown → site remains functional throughout

## Test Requirements

### Unit Tests (Jest + React Testing Library)

**Component Tests:**
- `components/__tests__/Hero.test.tsx` - Renders dual CTAs, modal opens on click, scroll works
- `components/__tests__/HolographicCard.test.tsx` - Renders with props, tilt effect on hover (desktop), static on mobile
- `components/__tests__/BlogList.test.tsx` - Renders MDX posts, filters by tag, pagination works
- `components/__tests__/BlogPost.test.tsx` - Renders MDX content, code blocks highlighted, metadata displays
- `components/__tests__/ArcReactor.test.tsx` - Renders SVG, pulse animation works, mouse parallax follows

**Utility Tests:**
- `utils/__tests__/deviceDetection.test.ts` - isMobile() detection, isWebGLSupported() detection
- `utils/__tests__/performance.test.ts` - measureFrameTime() thresholds, cooldown logic, particle disable/enable
- `content/blog/__tests__/schema.test.ts` - Zod validation accepts valid frontmatter, rejects missing fields, rejects invalid formats

**Shader Tests:**
- `components/3d/shaders/__tests__/Scanlines.test.tsx` - Renders scanline overlay, time-based drift works
- `components/3d/shaders/__tests__/Glow.test.tsx` - Bloom post-processing applies to blue elements
- `components/3d/shaders/__tests__/Particles.test.tsx` - Renders 50 particles, float speeds within range

### E2E Tests (Playwright)

**Critical User Journeys:**
- `e2e/vc-journey.spec.ts` - Complete VC path from landing to contact form
- `e2e/engineer-journey.spec.ts` - Complete engineer path from landing to blog deep-dive
- `e2e/mobile-experience.spec.ts` - Mobile rendering, performance, CSS-only fallback
- `e2e/webgl-context-loss.spec.ts` - Simulate context loss, verify fallback and recovery
- `e2e/keyboard-nav.spec.ts` - Tab through entire site, verify all interactions work without mouse
- `e2e/screen-reader.spec.ts` - NVDA/VoiceOver navigation, verify ARIA labels and announcements

### Integration Tests

**Blog Pipeline:**
- `tests/blog-pipeline.test.ts` - Create MDX post with frontmatter → build → verify RSS includes it → verify page renders → verify Zod catches invalid frontmatter

**Performance Tests:**
- `tests/lighthouse.ci.ts` - Lighthouse audit in CI, enforce 90+ mobile, 95+ desktop
- `tests/bundle-size.test.ts` - Monitor bundle size, alert if grows >10% from baseline

